# Run the linter after code changes

After editing `.gd` scripts (or other files covered by checks), run the linter before finishing:

```bash
python tools/run_checks.py --lint-only
```

Or: `make lint`

Do this even for small changes. Fix any gdlint issues before committing or reporting the task complete.

For substantive changes, prefer the full check suite when feasible:

```bash
python tools/run_checks.py
```

Or: `make check`
